Detailed Description

Abstract class for elements of a sequence in libgeoxml.

GeoXmlProjectLine, GeoXmlLineFlow, GeoXmlProgram, GeoXmlProgramParameter and GeoXmlCategory can be treated as a super class of GeoXmlSequence.

Function Documentation

int geoxml_sequence_previous ( GeoXmlSequence **  sequence  ) 

Use as an auxiliary function to geoxml_sequence_next.

Assign sequence to the previous sequence sequenced or NULL if there isn't.

Returns one of: GEOXML_RETV_SUCCESS, GEOXML_RETV_NULL_PTR, GEOXML_RETV_NOT_A_SEQUENCE

See also:
geoxml_sequence_next

int geoxml_sequence_next ( GeoXmlSequence **  sequence  ) 

Use to iterate over sequences.

Assign sequence to the next sequence sequenced or NULL if there isn't. Example: 

 GeoXmlSequence * i;
 geoxml_[parent]_get_[sequence]([parent], &i, 0);
 while (i != NULL) {
        ...
        geoxml_sequence_next(&i);
 }

Returns one of: GEOXML_RETV_SUCCESS, GEOXML_RETV_NULL_PTR, GEOXML_RETV_NOT_A_SEQUENCE

See also:
geoxml_sequence_previous

int geoxml_sequence_remove ( GeoXmlSequence *  sequence  ) 

Removes sequence from its sequence.

It is not deleted and can be reinserted into sequence using geoxml_sequence_prepend or geoxml_sequence_append.

A special case are the parameter. It cannot be removed if it belongs to an instanciated group. Also, if it is removed, all referenced parameters are automatically removed

Returns one of: GEOXML_RETV_SUCCESS, GEOXML_RETV_NULL_PTR, GEOXML_RETV_NOT_A_SEQUENCE, GEOXML_RETV_MORE_THAN_ONE_INSTANCES

gboolean geoxml_sequence_is_same_sequence ( GeoXmlSequence *  sequence,
GeoXmlSequence *  other 
)

Return TRUE if sequence and other are the same sequences.

Otherwise, return FALSE.

If sequence or other is NULL, returns FALSE.

Returns one of: GEOXML_RETV_SUCCESS, GEOXML_RETV_NULL_PTR, GEOXML_RETV_NOT_A_SEQUENCE, GEOXML_RETV_DIFFERENT_SEQUENCES

int geoxml_sequence_move_after ( GeoXmlSequence *  sequence,
GeoXmlSequence *  position 
)

Moves sequence to the position after position.

Returns one of: GEOXML_RETV_SUCCESS, GEOXML_RETV_NULL_PTR, GEOXML_RETV_NOT_A_SEQUENCE, GEOXML_RETV_DIFFERENT_SEQUENCES
